This page outlines the installation process for Prophet and SD.

* Install Prophet.
The following command will get you a copy of the source tree you can install:

>git clone git://gitorious.org/prophet/prophet.git

Once you've downloaded Prophet, you can install it:

>cd prophet

>PERL_MM_USE_DEFAULT=1 perl Makefile.PL

>make test

>make install

*  Install SD.

The following command will get you a copy of the source tree you can install:

> git clone git://gitorious.org/prophet/sd.git

Once you've downloaded SD, you can install it:

>cd sd

>PERL_MM_USE_DEFAULT=1 perl Makefile.PL

>make test

>make install

